entry.value: select cols.*, case when cons.column_name is NULL then 'N' else 'Y' end as primary_key from (select table_name as TableName,column_name as ColumnName , to_char(column_id) as ColumnPosition, data_type as COLUMNDATATYPE from user_tab_cols) cols LEFT JOIN (SELECT cols.table_name, cols.column_name FROM all_constraints cons, all_cons_columns cols WHERE cons.constraint_type = 'P' AND cons.constraint_name = cols.constraint_name AND cons.owner = cols.owner) cons on cols.TableName = cons.table_name and cols.ColumnName = cons.column_name where cols.TableName in (${'metadataTables'})
